import React from 'react'
import Carousel from 'react-bootstrap/Carousel';
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
import { Button, CardGroup, Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap';

export default function Comment_slider() {
    return (
        <Carousel>
            <Carousel.Item>
                <Row xs={2} md={4} className="g-5 my-5 d-flex justify-content-center">
                    {Array.from({ length: 3 }).map((_, idx) => (
                        <Col>
                            <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }} className='rounded-0 border-0'>
                                <Card.Img variant="top" src="https://superfood.qodeinteractive.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/fruit-home-image5.jpg" />
                                <Card.Body>
                                    <Card.Title>Card Title</Card.Title>
                                    <Card.Text>
                                        Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the
                                        bulk of the card's content.
                                    </Card.Text>
                                </Card.Body>
                            </Card>
                        </Col>
                    ))}
                </Row>
            </Carousel.Item>
            <Carousel.Item>
                <Row xs={2} md={4} className="g-5 my-5 d-flex justify-content-center">
                    {Array.from({ length: 3 }).map((_, idx) => (
                        <Col>
                            <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }} className='rounded-0 border-0'>
                                <Card.Img variant="top" src="https://superfood.qodeinteractive.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/fruit-home-image6.jpg" />
                                <Card.Body>
                                    <Card.Title>Card Title</Card.Title>
                                    <Card.Text>
                                        Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the
                                        bulk of the card's content.
                                    </Card.Text>
                                </Card.Body>
                            </Card>
                        </Col>
                    ))}
                </Row>
            </Carousel.Item>
        </Carousel>
    );
}
